# Environment Variables — Jokitugasku
# 
# CARA SETUP:
# 1. Buka https://supabase.com → masuk ke project kamu
# 2. Klik "Settings" (ikon gear) → pilih "API"
# 3. Copy nilai berikut:
#    - "Project URL"     → isi ke NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL
#    - "anon / public"   → isi ke NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#    - "service_role"    → isi ke SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
# 4. Simpan file ini sebagai ".env.local" (hapus ".example")
#
# GEMINI AI ASSISTANT (opsional tapi direkomendasikan):
# 1. Buka https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
# 2. Buat API key baru (gratis)
# 3. Isi ke GEMINI_API_KEY di bawah

NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://XXXXXXXXXXXX.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.XXXXXXXX
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.XXXXXXXX

# Google Gemini API Key (untuk AI Assistant)
# Dapatkan gratis di: https://aistudio.google.com/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyCWz_vMNnlu_wMde_9BA-LG98c-0sKHsTg